channel.title: Not Online?
channel.description:
MoparScape serverstatus page keeps saying my server is offline, when it is online.
I can log in on my computer, all the other computers in my house, and two of my friend's computers
But it still doesn't let me register it, cuz it says its offline, any help?

item.title: Not Online?
item.dc:creator: @jake_93 jake_93
item.description:
@jake_93 wrote:

After you tried adding your server to the server status page it should have gave you a ip, user and pass for it to connect to. (your server)
And also a site to visit.

You clearly need to visit the site.
You will need to Log into your server using the log in details provived but using the ip they asked you to.

Hope i helped,
